playstore_details.title: Ultra Fitness: Workouts & Meal Plans
playstore_details.description:
Are you looking to lose weight, build muscle or just get healthier? Well we’ve made the process easy to achieve. So you can enjoy working out, eat healthy and love the food you eat. 

Our team of Personal Trainers led by Kwame Dankwah; came together to identify how and why their clients achieved their transformation. After doing so they package that knowledge into an easy to use app with detailed workout programs and meal plans for you to follow and get the outcome you want.


INSPIRATION. INSTRUCTION. TRANSFORMATION

Workout with confidence with everything you need to get the results that you deserve. Use Ultra Fitness as your personal trainer and see your body transform fast!

APP FEATURES & BENEFITS

400+ Different Exercises
400+ Video Demonstrations with audio instructions 
40+ Workout Programs for: (weight loss, get healthy or build strength)
40+ Meal plans all designed around your goals
Track and measure Workout Progress
Email Support Training and Nutrition Tips

Commit to living a fitter, healthier lifestyle and transform your body today. Download the app now we want to you be our next success story! Get ready for more energy, more fat burning, more strength and more confidence with Ultra Fitness.

You speak, we listen! Constantly looking for ways to improve the app we will be happy to hear your thoughts or send us your transformation we love seeing results.

SUPPORT: info@ultra-fitness.co.uk
playstore_details.summary: Lose Weight or Build Muscle with the right workouts & recipes designed for you!
playstore_details.summaryHTML: Lose Weight or Build Muscle with the right workouts & recipes designed for you!

We understand how difficult it can be going through your fitness journey. We've gone through similar growing pains in trying to create an awesome app, to make things smoother and easier for you we've fixed some bugs. 

We hope you'll enjoy ;)
